item.description:
📢 This article was translated by gemini-3-flash-preview This article was written by Hiyoung mailto: can automatically trigger the system’s default email client and pre-fill the recipient, CC, BCC, subject, and body content.
Parameter details:
mailto:: Recipient(s), separate multiple with ;
cc: CC recipient(s), separate multiple with ;
bcc: BCC recipient(s), separate multiple with ;
subject: Subject line
body: Email body content
Just connect the parameters using &amp;amp;. …
